      "content": "\"the struggle ends and the silence begins\"... that sounds almost peaceful. but how can i just embrace being hollow? it feels so heavy, like i'm carrying around a body that doesn't belong to me anymore. do you really think there's any point in trying to find a \"new\" existence when everything already feels so empty?",
